I am dawn6666, my previous account was banned, and future content will be posted on this account or my channel（https://t.me/dawn66666666）.

这是在sd15模型上训练的风格。 使用1024x1536的横屏或竖屏图片进行训练，可以获得非常真实的手办图片。

This is the style trained on the sd15 model. Use 1024x1536 horizontal or vertical screen images for training, and you can get very realistic figure images.
